WILLIAM SHAKESPEARE’S MALMSEY ..................5. 2.99 2.49 27.95

According to Shakespeare, the Duke of Clarence was drowned in a butt of Malmsey. We are not suggesting that you buy a whole butt to rid this planet of your mortal enemies.
